PLACEHOLDER: speaker_change.mp3
Description: Subtle audio cue for smooth transitions between speakers
Suggested content: Gentle crossfade, soft click, or brief silence gap (0.2-0.4 seconds)
Usage: Triggered by [SFX: speaker_change] cues when switching between voices
Recommended volume: -24dB to -20dB normalized (very subtle)
Format: MP3, 128kbps minimum
